Easy Bookings

Whistle gives a user-friendly booking interface . This includes a clear descriptions of various car types available as per the number of people and many more.

Secure Payments

Whistle had integrated, secure payment gateways that let users complete transactions quickly, in a hassle-free manner.

{" "} Flexible Plans

Customers can maintaining their flexible plans for bookings according to their convenience.

Documents Required for Car Rental

If you’re planning a trip to the UAE you’ll find that all major attractions in the UAE are spread far and wide. From unique shopping destinations like the Mall Of The Emirates, popular landmarks such as the Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque in Abu Dhabi to exquisite hotels and resorts located in Ras Al Khaimah, the best way to get around is by car. You are eligible to rent a car across the emirates provided you have the below mentioned documents valid with you:

Local Residents

  • Local Driving License
  • Resident Visa

Tourists

  • Passpord
  • Resident Visa
